g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f282a4de9bbd9f1f03af522a85b6177672183d7c","tid":842001,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b5460cb4a4072f7da428aeadc72243f8b9c3d4","tid":842001,"uid":96894,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"要永續 Daddy 繼續留在曼聯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2df8dfd04984f2087f01f2a04b7e89b89c4ae1","tid":842001,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"摩佬咁垃圾去教傑志就差唔多"},{"pid":"b8d6fe02742dec7c684a2ca92cd9440f1946058a","tid":842001,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0045565abcecae1f34991ed1cf8bbb80e972a4f","tid":842001,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"69a5d167e2e83a9a31c4c2044e7a8c9341931353","tid":842001,"uid":29952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35842aa7da5d7c0060d237b41de090040d99dcff","tid":842001,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T03:04:40.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=VgDisFYbR%2F7l5trZ3dsCHARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=74aee7fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】據英國《每日郵報》指出，曼聯周末輸波後急忙乘火車回曼徹斯特，卻不見摩連奴的蹤影，更有傳摩帥今周內被炒。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯周六作客以1:3不敵韋斯咸，連同周中聯賽盃敗於打比郡連輸兩仗，加上中場保羅普巴與摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）訓練時引起爭執，令外界認為將帥不和的問題已浮面。英國傳媒拍到曼聯大軍輸波後選擇急急腳乘火車離開倫敦，返回曼徹斯特，但當中只有球員卻不見摩帥身影，引來更多揣測，不過亦有指摩帥因留在倫敦陪伴家人而未有隨行。<br />\n<br />\n事實上周六輸波後，錄得紅魔29年來的最差開季成績，開季7戰只得10分，更已落後宿敵曼城9分，外界認為摩連奴在曼聯的日子已進入倒數階段，更有傳周內被炒。雖然球會行政副總裁活華特曾表明不希望單純因成績而作出艱難的決定，加上下周歐聯戰線重開，時間上看來不是炒掉摩帥的合適時間，但球迷的不滿，以及差劣成績的確需要解決。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》又指，賽後將輸波責任歸咎於球證的摩帥，在賽後記者會只回答了3條問題就離去，然後就被新聞官帶走，並沒有回答被追問有關普巴的問題。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:35:26.000Z","msg":"快啦我屌你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"【BBC記者Simon Stone：摩連奴現階段不可能被炒｜體嘢報道】<br />\n<br />\n閱讀全文：<a href=\"https://wp.me/p75t7v-4V2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp75t7v-4V2&d=VgDisFYbR%2F7l5trZ3dsCHARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9ac8deec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wp.me/p75t7v-4V2</a><br />\n<br />\n即便曼聯面臨首七輪聯賽的第三場敗仗，但BBC記者Simon Stone表示，曼聯領隊摩連奴現階段不可能被炒。他引用三位前任領隊的例子，說明曼聯現在不會立即宣判他「死刑」。另一方面，〈Telegraph〉記者James Ducker引述曼聯高層的消息指，曼聯沒有接觸施丹接任主帥一職。<br />\n<br />\n挽留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"如果曼聯對華倫西亞輸波的話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f840d541a67c31e8b3f70820ae22c5f834ceaa6a","tid":842001,"uid":124941,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4ef84aff4dcebe3d14575f67f6ea0bff50f5f4d6","tid":842001,"uid":16451,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"37f0019fe7d130b81f6ea764d799b498b9fbed43","tid":842001,"uid":72415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff01d0c7f22a9c31a646dc7cba128d3e2623cb9e","tid":842001,"uid":16659,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/061a23efa7176399327e5b6d40b2fde5/tumblr_inline_pfnxl0147Y1snzz7w_540.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F061a23efa7176399327e5b6d40b2fde5%2Ftumblr_inline_pfnxl0147Y1snzz7w_540.gif&h=54fb266b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地暴聯上下都好有戲味<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:48:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"隻猩猩成日都忽忽地咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/154003_5776e1a85704e786344418c8dd60bef1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/